    "description": "Grapple Gunners is a fast-paced multiplayer experience about grappling hooks and guns! Play against friends and compete to be the winner in this action-packed PvP game!<br><br>In Grapple Gunners, you fight your friends to be the last one standing. Every round begins with everyone scrambling to get a weapon and starting to fight. Every player starts with a grappling hook to make their way around the map. The rounds are short but action-packed! Tons of weapons such as the Grenade Launcher, Laser Pistol and Minigun ensure that every round will end with chaos!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161230/extras/966600f0c3dd3d59436d6883df959851.poster.avif?t=1763957804\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161230/extras/966600f0c3dd3d59436d6883df959851.webm?t=1763957804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161230/extras/966600f0c3dd3d59436d6883df959851.mp4?t=1763957804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• Play online or locally with 2-4 players<br>• Fight across 30 different maps<br>• Customize your character to look however you please<br>• Game settings to customize your matches",
